.Dd $Mdocdate: June 16 2021 $
.Dt OCIIC 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ociic
.Nd OpenCores I2C controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "ociic* at fdt?"
.Cd "iic* at ociic?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the OpenCores I2C controller such as the
I2C controller integrated on the SiFive FU540/FU740 SoCs.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr iic 4 ,
.Xr intro 4
